of their own app.

00:58:59.320 --> 00:59:02.000
The reason why you want to
follow the design guide for

00:59:02.000 --> 00:59:04.960
all of the important principles
is that you may

00:59:04.960 --> 00:59:08.830
feel really good about having
consistency across all these

00:59:08.830 --> 00:59:10.540
different platforms,
but a user is

00:59:10.540 --> 00:59:11.970
only using one platform.

00:59:11.970 --> 00:59:12.640
