disadvantage.

00:59:23.650 --> 00:59:26.290
If you have a competitor that
is actually hewing closer to

00:59:26.290 --> 00:59:29.790
the design guide in terms of
metrics, contrast, even simple

00:59:29.790 --> 00:59:33.140
expected things like are our
tabs at the top or the bottom,

00:59:33.140 --> 00:59:35.840
your competitor all of a sudden
has an advantage.

00:59:35.840 --> 00:59:38.792
